 1. Formation   
    The formation of player on the field can 
indicates the target of some tactics . It is mainly 
based on the 3 position forwarders, midfielders, 
and defenders  [17]. Some formation is desig ned 
to pursue the defense or attack  [18]. Meaning 
that, the accounted gdg  score should base  on the 
previous game with the same current interested 
formation.   
 
2. Coach   
    In modern football, coach is one of the short 
lifecycle in football based on the team  [19]. 
Hence, the same team in season or period in gdg 
range may have different coach leading the team. 
The filtering process should cut the last previous 
match on the first game the current coach 
enrolled  [20].  
 
3. Squad Rotation   
    The team xG & xGA  is the summation of the 
current 11 player s on the team. It is appear ed that 
the squad rotation may twist the analytics results  
[21]. Hen ce, the analytics will account  for the xG 
& xGA  of the similar squad meaning the game 
with many switching in player should not be in 
typical game xG & xGA  analytics .
